# Resend API Key (for contact form email delivery)
# 1. Go to https://resend.com/
# 2. Create an account (free tier: 100 emails/day)
# 3. Create an API key
# 4. Add RESEND_API_KEY as an environment variable in your Vercel project settings
#
# Email flow:
# - Owner notification -> goldenboymoyo@gmail.com (branded HTML template)
# - Auto-reply -> form submitter's email (branded HTML template)
